   RowBox[{"AntennaSolve", "[", 
    RowBox[{"necFile", ",", "outFile"}], "]"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\n", 
   RowBox[{"(*", 
    RowBox[{"Print", " ", "the", " ", "results"}], "*)"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
